snippet.title: Stars and Stripes Cookies
snippet.description: Please your patriotic palate with these delectable, fun Stars and Stripes Cookies treats. Drizzled with red, white and blue icing, these star-shaped cookies are easy to prepare and taste great with milk or coffee.

snippet.title: NESTLÉ® TOLL HOUSE® Stars and Stripes Cookies
snippet.description: Celebrate the freedom to express your creativity with this recipe for NESTLÉ TOLL HOUSE Stars and Stripes Cookies. An inspired display of American pride - these star-shaped cookies are decorated with red juicy strawberries and plump blueberries on velvety white cream cheese - all topped with a sprinkle of chocolate chip mini morsels. These star-spangled cookies are the perfect Independence Day treat.

snippet.title: Lemon Sour Cream Stars
snippet.description: These festive lemon and sour cream star cookies are a fun addition to your holiday cookie repertoire.

snippet.title: CARNATION® Famous Fudge
snippet.description: The reviews are in! This five-star recipe makes an unforgettably delectable holiday gift – one family, friends, and coworkers won't soon forget. And with easy variations, you can make milk chocolate, butterscotch, or peanutty chocolate fudge.

snippet.title: Ovaltine Brownies
snippet.description: Ovaltine Brownies are perfect for picnics, family affairs and entertaining too. Great to serve for large gatherings.

snippet.title: Oatmeal Scotchies
snippet.description: The two ingredients which make these extraordinary cookies special are the combination of oats and butterscotch chips. These Oatmeal Scotchies will disappear from your cookie jar in no time.

snippet.title: Original NESTLÉ® TOLL HOUSE® Chocolate Chip Cookies
snippet.description: This famous classic American cookie is a treat no matter what the age or occasion. Enjoy it with a glass of cold milk.

snippet.title: Sugar Cookie Holiday Trees
snippet.description: Sugar Cookie Holiday Trees are sweet treats and easy-to-make decorations too! Simply cut stars out of our Toll House Sugar Cookie Dough Tub using different sized cookie cutters, then bake, stack, decorate and admire!

snippet.title: Quick Eggs Benedict
snippet.description: This quick variation of eggs benedict takes just 15 minutes to prepare and will delight your guests with its rich flavors.

snippet.title: Chocolate Lover's Cookies
snippet.description: If you are looking for Valentine cookies with a double-dose of chocolate, these Chocolate Lover's Cookies might be just the thing.
